palette.title: Five Things About Me
palette.description:
1. I met my best friend, Annie, when we both worked at Woolworths. I worked there for 4 months (the store closed). In September, it will be 30 years since Annie and I met. We are still best friends. : ) 2. My favorite song for the last 49 years has been "Puff The Magic Dragon". 3. I am a HUGE Science Fiction geek. 4. We have bird feeders on our deck. I love seeing all the different birds, but my favorites are the Gold Finches. 5. I love the sky. Day sky, blue sky, stormy sky, cloudy sky, sunset sky, night sky, every sky.
I am tagging:
